_:N7970e4cf923a4ebab597e11ccf7c03a7 <http://schema.org/description> "The National Lottery Community Fund awards money raised by National Lottery players to communities across the UK, working with local groups and UK-wide charities, enabling people and communities to thrive. The National Lottery Community Fund is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport ." .
